    Page: 127-128
By: Mechthild of Magdeburg
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Contemptus Mundi
---
I know now as 1 have known before that I must learn to drink many cups of
gall to the dregs for alas! the devil has many friends among spiritual
people, who are so full of poison that they not only drink it themselves but
must needs hand it in bitterness to the children of God.
